included.customDescription: A report I put together for one round of testing of a mobile game. I was the Research Lead on this project, meaning I worked with the game designers, programmer, and artist to design the research plan. This process required me to determine what information from users that the development team would find most valuable according to the phase the game was in. Then, I executed the research through moderating and recording all relevant data. This is an example of a report I created after each round.
A research plan I created for user testing of a mobile game in alpha phase. The plan includes Research Objectives, Testing Methods, Session Structure, and a moderator introduction script and notes.

I aspire to work at a progressive technology company where I can utilize my education and experience in the UX industry and apply it to various categories of real world problem solving.
